The MSI Bravo 15 and 17 gaming laptops combine the most advanced 7nm AMD Ryzen processors and Radeon RX graphics, providing stunning performance and a smooth gaming display with FreeSync Premium support. Immersive Hi-Res Audio then offers a seamless audio experience, while MSI’s exclusive Cooler Boost 5 thermal solution will keep your notebook cool under the most demanding of tasks. With these game-ready features, you will be ready to conquer any battle. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-377302" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MSI-Bravo-image-1-640x360.png" alt="MSI Bravo image 1" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MSI-Bravo-image-1-640x360.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MSI-Bravo-image-1-600x337.png 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MSI-Bravo-image-1-768x432.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MSI-Bravo-image-1.png 941w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The MSI Bravo 15 and 17 laptops inherit the spirit of the Thunderbird logo by offering innovative features and great performance. In fact, their performance is their biggest selling point – as they are equipped with the latest AMD Ryzen 4000 H-Series Mobile Processors which offer double the power efficiency of the previous generation. They also use AMD Radeon RX 5000 series mobile GPUs to ensure you get incredible performance in a range of games when playing at 1080p. Additionally, the Bravo 15 and 17 laptops are equipped with 120Hz and 144Hz displays respectively, both of which use AMD’s FreeSync Premium technology to ensure you have a fluid, tear-free gaming experience. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-377304" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MSI-Bravo-image-2-430x430.png" alt="MSI Bravo image 2" width="640" 